Follow this guide:
https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Fontconfig#Infinality


Key points:
1) eselect fontconfig enable 52-infinality.conf
2) eselect infinality set ultimate-free
3) eselect lcdfilter set ultimate

- Make sure to disable all settings in fontconfig other 
  than 52-infinality.conf

- If you want ultimate-ms compile
  media-fonts/infinality-ultimate-meta 
  with +ms flag
